The '''Lullaby Motel''' was a sleazy establishment on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Harridan (planet)|Harridan]], just outside [[Spaceport City]]'s spaceport's bulk cargo gate. Two [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] posing as newlyweds [[Henry Buntwhistle]] and [[Martha Buntwhistle]] once signed into this motel in order to get in contact with [[Egot Pai-4-Yem]].

